com.atmecs.falcon.automation.verifyresult

Class VerificationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atmecs.falcon.automation.verifyresult.VerificationManager

  • public class VerificationManager
extends java.lang.Object
    VerificationManager class implements all type of verification methods. 1. Verify two integer values 2. Verify two string values 3. Verify two boolean values 4. Verify two JSON object 5. Verify true/false condition
